Vulnerability description:
These days Captcha's are one of the most vulnerable methods To Protect The Website From Bots.
The Captcha Response is not validated on the server-side when submitting a Signup form to the endpoint.

Steps To Reproduce:
1. example.com/signup
2. Fill the input field and Validate the captcha.
3. Turn on Proxy(Burp, ZAP) submit form and capture the request.


Impact:
An Attacker use this Create fake accounts and full you database with unnecessary data.
